oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Andrews Tabernacle Christian Methodist Episicopal Church
306 Woods Ferry Road, Highway 109, Lebanon, TN

Black and white photograph of a white church with wood siding, gable roof and one-story porch; porch has two white double doors with lamp in peak of porch roof; stone steps with black metal leading up to front doors
Andrews Tabernacle Christian Methodist Episicopal Church was established in 1897.
